    <title>JDK配置</title>
    <url>/JDK%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE.html</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/hint.css/2.4.1/hint.min.css"><p><em>工欲善其事必先利其器</em></p>
<hr>
<h3 id="下载"><a href="#下载" class="headerlink" title="下载"></a>下载</h3><ol>
<li><a href="https://www.oracle.com/java/technologies/javase-downloads.html">oracle 官网</a>下载对应安装包</li>
<li>按照步骤按照所有需要安装的版本</li>
</ol>
<h3 id="电脑环境"><a href="#电脑环境" class="headerlink" title="电脑环境"></a>电脑环境</h3><blockquote>
<p>Mac</p>
</blockquote>
<h3 id="安装"><a href="#安装" class="headerlink" title="安装"></a>安装</h3><blockquote>
<p>使用安装包点击安装或者使用bin包安装</p>
</blockquote>
<ol>
<li>查看已安装的版本</li>
</ol>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 安装包 dmg</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">cd</span> /Library/Java/JavaVirtualMachines</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<ol start="2">
<li>查看本地 java_home</li>
</ol>
<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">/usr/libexec/java_home</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<ol start="3">
<li>修改配置文件</li>
</ol>
<p>在 OS X 下，java也就是/usr/bin/java在默认情况下指向的是已经安装的最新版本。但是你可以设置环境变量JAVA_HOME来更改其指向</p>
<h3 id="环境配置"><a href="#环境配置" class="headerlink" title="环境配置"></a>环境配置</h3><p>使用bin包安装</p>
<p>环境切换</p>
<p>配置文件 加载顺序</p>
<blockquote>
<ul>
<li>/etc/profile </li>
<li>/etc/paths </li>
<li>~/.bash_profile </li>
<li>~/.bash_login </li>
<li>~/.profile </li>
<li>~/.bashrc</li>
</ul>
</blockquote>
<p>在<del>/.bash_profile（如果是Zsh，修改</del>/.zshrc）文件中添加如下内容：</p>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">vim ~/.zshrc</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>



<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># jdk</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">export</span> JAVA_17_HOME=<span class="string">&quot;/Users/admin/software/JDK/jdk-17.jdk/Contents/Home&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">export</span> JAVA_11_HOME=<span class="string">&quot;/Users/admin/software/JDK/jdk-11.0.13.jdk/Contents/Home&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">export</span> JAVA_8301_HOME=<span class="string">&quot;/Library/Java/JavaVirtualMachines/jdk1.8.0_301.jdk/Contents/Home&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">export</span> JAVA_8311_HOME=<span class="string">&quot;/Library/Java/JavaVirtualMachines/jdk1.8.0_311.jdk/Contents/Home&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">export</span> JAVA_HOME=<span class="variable">$JAVA_8311_HOME</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">#alias命令动态切换JDK版本</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">alias</span> jdk17=<span class="string">&quot;export JAVA_HOME=<span class="variable">$JAVA_17_HOME</span>&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">alias</span> jdk11=<span class="string">&quot;export JAVA_HOME=<span class="variable">$JAVA_11_HOME</span>&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">alias</span> jdk8=<span class="string">&quot;export JAVA_HOME=<span class="variable">$JAVA_8311_HOME</span>&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">alias</span> jdk8301=<span class="string">&quot;export JAVA_HOME=<span class="variable">$JAVA_8301_HOME</span>&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line">PATH=<span class="variable">$PATH</span>:<span class="variable">$JAVA_HOME</span>/bin</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">export</span> PATH</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 使配置生效</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">source</span> ~/.zshrc</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h3 id="验证"><a href="#验证" class="headerlink" title="验证"></a>验证</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">java -version</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>



<h3 id="卸载"><a href="#卸载" class="headerlink" title="卸载"></a>卸载</h3><ol>
<li><p>打开终端</p>
</li>
<li><p>输入 </p>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sudo rm -fr /Library/Internet\ Plug-Ins/JavaAppletPlugin.plugin </span><br><span class="line">sudo rm -fr /Library/PreferencesPanes/JavaControlPanel.prefpane</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li>
<li><p>查找当前版本 </p>
</li>
</ol>
<p>​         输入：ls /Library/Java/JavaVirtualMachines/ </p>
<p>​         输出：==jdk-9.0.1==.jdk</p>
<ol start="4">
<li><p>输入        </p>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sudo rm -rf /Library/Java/JavaVirtualMachines/jdk-9.0.1.jdk  </span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li>
</ol>
<h3 id="官方文档"><a href="#官方文档" class="headerlink" title="官方文档"></a>官方文档</h3><blockquote>
<p>JDK API文档</p>
<p><a href="http://www.oracle.com/technetwork/java/javase/documentation/jdk8-doc-downloads-2133158.html">java SE 8 API文档</a></p>
<p><a href="http://docs.oracle.com/javase/8/docs/api/index.html">jdk-8-apidocs 在线版</a></p>
<p><a href="http://www.oracle.com/technetwork/java/javase/documentation/java-se-7-doc-download-435117.html">java SE 7 API文档</a></p>
<p><a href="http://www.oracle.com/technetwork/java/javase/downloads/jdk-6u25-doc-download-355137.html">java SE 6 API文档</a></p>
<p><a href="http://docs.oracle.com/javase/8/docs/">Java Platform Standard Edition 8 Documentation</a></p>
</blockquote>
]]></content>
